1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

2
00:00:12,992 --> 00:00:15,370
Let Geon-woo return
to exactly the way he used to be.

3
00:00:17,831 --> 00:00:19,249
That's my wish.

4
00:00:19,749 --> 00:00:22,210
Doctor! He is breathing on his own!

5
00:00:22,293 --> 00:00:23,503
I need you to come now.

6
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:28,174
WISH GRANTED

7
00:00:39,227 --> 00:00:42,230
Ha-joon, come to me.
I need to see you in person to help you.

8
00:00:45,525 --> 00:00:46,526
Let's go, Se-ah.

9
00:00:47,902 --> 00:00:49,946
There's someone we need to meet.

10
00:00:54,951 --> 00:00:55,910
My sister.

11
00:00:56,494 --> 00:00:59,455
Are you talking about Ha-young?

12
00:01:00,123 --> 00:01:00,957
Yeah.

13
00:01:01,541 --> 00:01:03,001
Didn't she go abroad to study?

14
00:01:05,086 --> 00:01:06,171
I lied.

15
00:01:07,213 --> 00:01:11,551
I was annoyed and embarrassed
that my sister quit her good job,

16
00:01:11,634 --> 00:01:13,845
changed her name, and became a shaman.

17
00:01:14,345 --> 00:01:15,346
A shaman?

18
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:16,514
That's why I lied.

19
00:01:40,580 --> 00:01:42,040
Damn it.

20
00:01:42,624 --> 00:01:43,708
Is this the right way?

21
00:01:44,209 --> 00:01:46,377
Yes, please follow the GPS.

22
00:01:46,461 --> 00:01:47,962
I'd appreciate it, sir.

23
00:01:48,046 --> 00:01:49,464
Seriously.

24
00:01:49,547 --> 00:01:51,591
I shouldn't have taken this call.

25
00:01:52,091 --> 00:01:52,926
This is…

26
00:02:06,981 --> 00:02:09,484
Hey, I can't go any further.

27
00:02:17,742 --> 00:02:18,826
Ha-joon.

28
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:20,662
Are you sure this is the right way?

29
00:02:21,412 --> 00:02:22,622
I think it is.

30
00:02:23,915 --> 00:02:24,916
Follow me carefully.

31
00:03:05,373 --> 00:03:06,207
Ha-joon.

32
00:03:06,958 --> 00:03:07,792
Yeah?

33
00:03:10,461 --> 00:03:12,213
Are you really sure it's this way?

34
00:03:13,631 --> 00:03:14,465
Yeah.

35
00:03:21,764 --> 00:03:22,682
Bugs!

36
00:03:22,765 --> 00:03:24,142
-Se-ah, wait up!
-Bugs!

37
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:33,067
Se-ah, hold up! Se-ah…

38
00:03:37,405 --> 00:03:38,406
Where are we?

39
00:03:50,209 --> 00:03:51,044
Se-ah.

40
00:04:17,987 --> 00:04:22,075
IF WISHES COULD KILL

41
00:04:25,161 --> 00:04:26,954
Are you sure someone lives here?

42
00:04:27,538 --> 00:04:28,623
I guess so.

43
00:04:29,957 --> 00:04:30,958
You guess so?

44
00:04:32,251 --> 00:04:33,628
You said you've been here.

45
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,880
I've never been inside.

46
00:04:37,757 --> 00:04:38,633
What?

47
00:04:41,427 --> 00:04:45,264
There's this weird guy in the house
who guards the place like a totem pole.

48
00:04:45,848 --> 00:04:48,226
Every time I come here,
he blocks the door and says,

49
00:04:48,309 --> 00:04:50,228
"Sorry, only guests may enter."

50
00:04:50,311 --> 00:04:53,398
What guest is more important
than a brother visiting his sister?

51
00:04:53,481 --> 00:04:55,525
Exactly! He just won't listen.

52
00:04:55,608 --> 00:04:58,277
I told him I wouldn't go in
and to send my sister outside.

53
00:04:58,361 --> 00:04:59,404
You know what he said?

54
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:02,198
He said that if my sister came outside,

55
00:05:03,032 --> 00:05:04,117
she would die.

56
00:05:05,118 --> 00:05:07,203
He could've just said she didn't want to.

57
00:05:08,371 --> 00:05:10,289
But what I really hate is…

58
00:05:11,165 --> 00:05:13,209
You know what that totem pole calls me?

59
00:05:17,755 --> 00:05:18,589
Brother-in-law.

60
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:22,343
I told you not to call me that.

61
00:05:23,386 --> 00:05:24,220
Hello.

62
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:31,102
Please come in. Come in, brother-in-law.

63
00:05:36,732 --> 00:05:38,359
Shall we pick up the pace a little?

64
00:05:38,443 --> 00:05:39,902
Brother-in-law, your sister--

65
00:05:39,986 --> 00:05:41,362
I'm not your brother-in-law.

66
00:05:41,446 --> 00:05:45,366
My bad. You said you were coming, Ha-joon,
so she's been waiting all day.

67
00:05:45,450 --> 00:05:46,284
Don't touch me.

68
00:05:46,367 --> 00:05:47,368
Let's hurry along.

69
00:05:48,286 --> 00:05:49,954
GEON-WOO

70
00:05:54,792 --> 00:05:55,877
Hello?

71
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,712
Hey, Geon-woo.

72
00:05:57,795 --> 00:06:00,173
Se-ah, why have you been so hard to reach?

73
00:06:01,716 --> 00:06:03,301
I've looked for you everywhere.

74
00:06:03,801 --> 00:06:05,553
You know I moved rooms, right?

75
00:06:06,053 --> 00:06:07,472
So why aren't you coming?

76
00:06:07,555 --> 00:06:08,389
Geon-woo.

77
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:10,141
The thing is,

78
00:06:10,224 --> 00:06:12,810
I'm a bit far away right now.

79
00:06:12,894 --> 00:06:14,479
Never mind. I'll come to you.

80
00:06:14,562 --> 00:06:15,771
Where are you right now?

81
00:06:16,939 --> 00:06:17,773
Se-ah.

82
00:06:18,941 --> 00:06:19,942
Se-ah?

83
00:06:21,861 --> 00:06:23,654
Where should I go?

84
00:06:24,363 --> 00:06:26,032
Where are you?

85
00:06:29,494 --> 00:06:30,703
Don't answer him!

86
00:06:42,507 --> 00:06:44,467
Fucking hell! I asked where you are!

87
00:06:45,092 --> 00:06:45,927
What's going on?

88
00:06:46,552 --> 00:06:48,763
-Answer me now.
-Can you lower your right hand?

89
00:06:52,058 --> 00:06:53,184
You can't move your arm?

90
00:06:57,188 --> 00:06:58,064
Bangwool, the rope!

91
00:06:58,147 --> 00:06:59,732
Right. Brother-in-law, don't move.

92
00:07:00,233 --> 00:07:01,067
Don't move!

93
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:04,529
If you keep ignoring me, I'll rip out
your boyfriend's tongue instead.

94
00:07:04,612 --> 00:07:06,155
He can't do that. Ignore him.

95
00:07:06,739 --> 00:07:08,491
Remember how your boyfriend went berserk?

96
00:07:09,575 --> 00:07:12,286
Should I try smashing his skull open
this time?

97
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:14,497
-What's going on?
-Brother-in-law, please!

98
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:16,582
-What's that for?
-It's dangerous!

99
00:07:16,666 --> 00:07:18,918
-What is?
-Just trust your sister!

100
00:07:22,129 --> 00:07:23,923
You think this will keep you alive?

101
00:07:25,132 --> 00:07:28,177
You, your boyfriend. I'll kill you all.

102
00:07:33,307 --> 00:07:34,725
You wanna play with me, huh?

103
00:07:36,561 --> 00:07:37,562
Se-ah.

104
00:07:39,855 --> 00:07:41,065
Se-ah!

105
00:07:43,985 --> 00:07:44,986
Yoo Se-ah!

106
00:07:57,957 --> 00:07:59,542
-What was that?
-To the altar!

107
00:07:59,625 --> 00:08:00,459
Don't touch Se-ah!

108
00:08:00,543 --> 00:08:03,170
What happened to Se-ah?
What did you just do to her?

109
00:08:04,589 --> 00:08:07,383
Her soul has been trapped.
I have to go bring her back.

110
00:08:07,466 --> 00:08:08,801
What do you even mean?

111
00:08:08,884 --> 00:08:12,179
There's no time to explain.
If I don't get her out now, she'll die.

112
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:18,060
Don't leave this room
until Bangwool signals you from outside.

113
00:08:18,144 --> 00:08:20,521
No matter what happens outside,

114
00:08:20,605 --> 00:08:22,023
do not come out.

115
00:09:05,608 --> 00:09:08,277
Haetsal, leave what happens outside to me.

116
00:09:08,361 --> 00:09:10,529
You just focus on things inside, okay?

117
00:09:19,747 --> 00:09:21,165
Don't worry.

118
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,426
Descendant of the Yoo family,
18 years old.

119
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:34,553
Her name is Se-ah.

120
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,698
The living bear three souls,
the dead three spirits.

121
00:09:53,781 --> 00:09:56,158
If even a single soul is missing,
one cannot exist.

122
00:09:56,242 --> 00:09:59,203
Open the soul gate to the soul,
the spirit gate to the spirit.

123
00:09:59,286 --> 00:10:02,206
Let the soul enter the soul vessel,
the spirit the spirit vessel.

124
00:10:02,748 --> 00:10:05,876
Cast all ill fortune and all foul things
beyond the orijeong.

125
00:10:06,502 --> 00:10:10,297
I pray and pray again
that you embrace only our child's soul.

126
00:10:12,466 --> 00:10:13,592
Se-ah.

127
00:10:15,428 --> 00:10:16,846
Se-ah, come to me.

128
00:10:18,264 --> 00:10:19,432
Se-ah.

129
00:10:22,852 --> 00:10:23,936
Se-ah!

130
00:10:49,211 --> 00:10:50,129
Se-ah.

131
00:10:50,629 --> 00:10:51,964
Se-ah, it's me.

132
00:10:54,049 --> 00:10:56,469
Don't you know who I am?
I'm Ha-joon's sister.

133
00:10:56,552 --> 00:10:58,846
Ha-young?

134
00:10:58,929 --> 00:11:00,014
Yes, that's right.

135
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:08,564
Where are we?

136
00:11:08,647 --> 00:11:10,524
It's the realm of the curse upon you.

137
00:11:12,193 --> 00:11:13,277
Don't worry, Se-ah.

138
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,446
I came here to get you out of here.

139
00:11:15,529 --> 00:11:18,073
Go through the door with me
and pass three rooms,

140
00:11:18,157 --> 00:11:19,325
and you can get out.

141
00:11:22,077 --> 00:11:23,370
The door…

142
00:11:24,705 --> 00:11:26,165
Where is it?

143
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,168
Bangwool, we're going in.

144
00:11:48,729 --> 00:11:50,606
Save us.

145
00:11:51,732 --> 00:11:53,317
The god of gates.

146
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,277
The goddess of fire and hearth.

147
00:11:55,361 --> 00:11:56,862
The god of our households.

148
00:11:56,946 --> 00:11:58,906
The god of our front gates and pillars.

149
00:11:58,989 --> 00:12:00,991
Guard us.

150
00:12:01,075 --> 00:12:03,786
Guard me, O gods.

151
00:13:16,901 --> 00:13:19,111
Before you go in,
you must promise me one thing.

152
00:13:20,988 --> 00:13:22,740
Once you go through the door,

153
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:25,367
you must never look back.

154
00:13:25,993 --> 00:13:28,871
In the cursed realm,
if you see me, it will see me too.

155
00:13:30,497 --> 00:13:31,582
"It"?

156
00:13:31,665 --> 00:13:34,251
The thing that killed your friend
and brought you here.

157
00:13:36,462 --> 00:13:39,381
If it sees me,
the doors I made will disappear.

158
00:13:39,465 --> 00:13:42,509
Then do I have to go by myself?

159
00:13:42,593 --> 00:13:44,803
Do you see the silk thread
around your wrist?

160
00:13:48,307 --> 00:13:50,559
This is the proof
that you and I are connected.

161
00:13:50,643 --> 00:13:54,188
The door leading out of the room
will be beyond the moment you fear.

162
00:13:55,731 --> 00:13:57,107
It won't be easy,

163
00:13:57,775 --> 00:13:59,610
but have faith that I'm right behind you.

164
00:14:02,029 --> 00:14:03,238
You can do this, Se-ah.

165
00:14:09,161 --> 00:14:10,245
Haetsal.

166
00:14:10,329 --> 00:14:13,499
The incense is burning faster today.
The doors will close quickly.

167
00:14:13,999 --> 00:14:15,042
Be careful.

168
00:14:19,964 --> 00:14:23,926
Having received the command
of the god of life and wealth,

169
00:14:24,009 --> 00:14:27,221
when Haetsal takes her seat,

170
00:14:27,304 --> 00:14:28,931
may the evil at the doorway…

171
00:16:43,190 --> 00:16:45,442
NURSE'S OFFICE

172
00:17:27,067 --> 00:17:29,570
Before you go in,
you must promise me one thing.

173
00:17:30,445 --> 00:17:32,447
Once you go through the door,

174
00:17:32,531 --> 00:17:34,616
you must never look back.

175
00:17:37,744 --> 00:17:38,871
Don't look back.

176
00:17:39,371 --> 00:17:40,831
Don't look back.

177
00:18:14,823 --> 00:18:15,824
Se-ah.

178
00:18:36,386 --> 00:18:37,221
Girigo.

179
00:18:37,304 --> 00:18:38,680
A perfect score in math…

180
00:18:38,764 --> 00:18:40,390
I said fucking get lost!

181
00:19:06,833 --> 00:19:07,834
Hyeong-wook.

182
00:19:18,762 --> 00:19:19,763
Help me!

183
00:19:23,976 --> 00:19:24,977
Se-ah.

184
00:19:36,321 --> 00:19:37,614
Please help me.

185
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:42,035
I don't want to die.

186
00:19:44,121 --> 00:19:45,205
Se-ah.

187
00:19:45,706 --> 00:19:46,581
Save me.

188
00:19:49,835 --> 00:19:51,211
Please help me.

189
00:19:51,295 --> 00:19:52,296
Hyeong-wook.

190
00:20:01,972 --> 00:20:03,849
Please! Se-ah!

191
00:20:06,768 --> 00:20:08,478
Please stop!

192
00:20:08,562 --> 00:20:10,772
Stop it!

193
00:20:10,856 --> 00:20:13,317
Se-ah!

194
00:21:09,414 --> 00:21:11,124
Stop. Help me.

195
00:21:18,632 --> 00:21:19,800
Se-ah.

196
00:21:19,883 --> 00:21:22,010
Something really strange
happened to me today.

197
00:21:23,136 --> 00:21:25,055
I talked to you on the phone today.

198
00:21:26,139 --> 00:21:27,516
Well, technically,

199
00:21:27,599 --> 00:21:30,769
I just heard you
talking to the other guys.

200
00:21:33,063 --> 00:21:34,648
But it wasn't you.

201
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:50,330
You're not Hyeong-wook.

202
00:21:53,125 --> 00:21:54,918
My friend was crying.

203
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:58,505
You piece of trash.

204
00:22:14,438 --> 00:22:16,440
Get lost!

205
00:23:01,026 --> 00:23:02,360
Bangwool, we're moving on.

206
00:23:23,673 --> 00:23:26,593
The bridges from the four divine ones.

207
00:23:26,676 --> 00:23:28,970
Even as you come,
misfortune follows, besieging us.

208
00:23:29,054 --> 00:23:31,181
Even as you come to this house,
misfortune follows.

209
00:23:31,264 --> 00:23:33,683
Even as the poor spirit comes,
misfortune follows.

210
00:23:33,767 --> 00:23:36,019
The Jade Emperor above,
the Underworld King below…

211
00:24:21,481 --> 00:24:24,693
Dad. For my first middle-school win,

212
00:24:25,694 --> 00:24:26,903
what will you get me?

213
00:24:41,418 --> 00:24:42,919
Dad.

214
00:24:43,712 --> 00:24:44,754
Yeah.

215
00:24:56,016 --> 00:24:58,310
What should I get you, sweetheart?

216
00:25:07,152 --> 00:25:08,403
Se-ah.

217
00:25:12,907 --> 00:25:14,034
Se-ah.

218
00:25:19,789 --> 00:25:20,874
Se-ah,

219
00:25:20,957 --> 00:25:23,001
your dad's driving.

220
00:25:31,343 --> 00:25:32,636
Mom.

221
00:25:33,136 --> 00:25:33,970
Honey!

222
00:25:48,693 --> 00:25:50,487
Se-ah, we have to go.

223
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:21,101
Se-ah.

224
00:26:21,685 --> 00:26:23,144
It's you, isn't it?

225
00:26:23,812 --> 00:26:26,356
We don't have time. Please.

226
00:26:26,439 --> 00:26:27,649
We must go to the door.

227
00:26:42,205 --> 00:26:45,458
Less than a third left.
If you can't make it, I'll pull you out.

228
00:26:45,542 --> 00:26:49,587
No one should be left in there alone.
I'll take off my mask if I have to.

229
00:26:49,671 --> 00:26:51,339
No!

230
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:52,841
No, Haetsal!

231
00:26:54,509 --> 00:26:57,137
What if you face it without the mask
and get trapped too?

232
00:26:57,887 --> 00:26:59,013
Haetsal, I…

233
00:27:00,515 --> 00:27:01,725
I can't bear to see that.

234
00:27:04,018 --> 00:27:05,270
For God's sake. Please.

235
00:27:08,314 --> 00:27:10,442
NA-RI

236
00:27:16,698 --> 00:27:18,533
Se-ah, baby girl…

237
00:27:18,616 --> 00:27:19,534
Mom.

238
00:27:19,617 --> 00:27:24,581
We didn't get to do much for you
before we had to leave you so soon.

239
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:28,460
I'm so sorry.

240
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:33,339
I felt so bad for you
that I couldn't leave this place…

241
00:27:35,633 --> 00:27:37,343
and waited for you all this time.

242
00:27:39,929 --> 00:27:41,097
My baby girl.

243
00:27:42,432 --> 00:27:45,977
Can you show me your face just once
so I can see

244
00:27:46,060 --> 00:27:47,812
how well you've grown?

245
00:27:49,564 --> 00:27:51,274
When the door closes, you're done.

246
00:27:51,357 --> 00:27:54,611
At least you should get out
so we can find a way, right?

247
00:27:57,113 --> 00:27:58,281
GIRIGO INSTALLED
OPEN

248
00:27:58,364 --> 00:28:00,909
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

249
00:28:02,744 --> 00:28:04,037
NOVEMBER 24, 2008
KANG

250
00:28:04,829 --> 00:28:05,997
Mom.

251
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:11,169
I'm sorry.

252
00:28:15,590 --> 00:28:16,800
Se-ah!

253
00:28:16,883 --> 00:28:18,343
If you don't look this way,

254
00:28:18,426 --> 00:28:20,553
I'll be tormented here forever!

255
00:28:21,054 --> 00:28:21,930
Se-ah!

256
00:28:22,013 --> 00:28:22,847
Look this way!

257
00:28:22,931 --> 00:28:24,140
Look at me!

258
00:28:24,933 --> 00:28:26,017
Se-ah!

259
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:28,353
If you don't look back now,

260
00:28:28,436 --> 00:28:31,397
your dad and I will burn to death here!

261
00:28:32,273 --> 00:28:34,108
We'll both burn to death!

262
00:28:34,192 --> 00:28:37,278
Se-ah! Look this way!

263
00:28:40,949 --> 00:28:42,116
Se-ah.

264
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,076
Se-ah.

265
00:28:43,827 --> 00:28:45,036
Se-ah, are you okay?

266
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:48,414
Do you wanna get up?

267
00:28:52,293 --> 00:28:54,087
It's okay. Breathe.

268
00:28:58,299 --> 00:28:59,133
You did well.

269
00:28:59,634 --> 00:29:01,052
Welcome back, Se-ah.

270
00:29:01,135 --> 00:29:03,429
I shouldn't have asked you
to come see my sister.

271
00:29:04,222 --> 00:29:05,765
I'm sorry for all this trouble.

272
00:29:06,432 --> 00:29:07,433
And Ha-young?

273
00:29:07,517 --> 00:29:09,310
She changed clothes and is resting.

274
00:29:10,061 --> 00:29:11,771
Seems like Haetsal had a rough time.

275
00:29:14,566 --> 00:29:16,609
Se-ah, can you hear me?

276
00:29:21,531 --> 00:29:23,324
Do you still hear a voice?

277
00:29:24,826 --> 00:29:26,870
Don't answer. Just listen.

278
00:29:28,371 --> 00:29:29,539
Is someone behind you?

279
00:29:30,123 --> 00:29:31,291
Se-ah, try to think.

280
00:29:31,791 --> 00:29:33,293
This is the third space.

281
00:29:33,835 --> 00:29:35,879
What is it? What's going on?

282
00:29:35,962 --> 00:29:37,881
Something clung to her
from the other side.

283
00:29:37,964 --> 00:29:40,466
When the door collapsed,
I think it came over with you.

284
00:29:41,593 --> 00:29:44,304
Notice how I'm not here.
Ask them to call for me.

285
00:29:45,221 --> 00:29:47,140
They can't because I'm behind the mask.

286
00:29:47,891 --> 00:29:50,518
Can you call Ha-young for me?

287
00:29:50,602 --> 00:29:52,228
-I'll go get--
-No, brother-in-law.

288
00:29:53,146 --> 00:29:54,772
It's looking for Haetsal, right?

289
00:29:55,565 --> 00:29:57,692
It senses her weakness
and is trying to attack.

290
00:30:01,654 --> 00:30:03,114
Something nasty clung to you.

291
00:30:06,284 --> 00:30:08,661
Se-ah, listen to me carefully.

292
00:30:08,745 --> 00:30:12,206
Haetsal told you not to look back
once you go through the door, right?

293
00:30:12,290 --> 00:30:14,083
In case those things see Haetsal.

294
00:30:14,167 --> 00:30:15,668
But you have to look back now.

295
00:30:17,879 --> 00:30:19,756
Then I can see them and deal with them.

296
00:30:19,839 --> 00:30:21,090
You mustn't look back.

297
00:30:21,174 --> 00:30:23,426
Don't let him fool you.
Find the door and get out.

298
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,809
Don't go out the door.

299
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:34,812
You collapsed at the gate
when you came in, remember?

300
00:30:34,896 --> 00:30:35,939
Se-ah, please!

301
00:30:36,022 --> 00:30:37,732
You have to keep your head.

302
00:30:37,815 --> 00:30:39,400
-You have to get out.
-Stay here!

303
00:30:40,485 --> 00:30:41,694
Get out, quickly!

304
00:30:42,487 --> 00:30:43,613
Listen to me!

305
00:30:44,322 --> 00:30:46,532
I don't know.

306
00:30:47,033 --> 00:30:48,493
I don't know!

307
00:30:50,995 --> 00:30:51,996
What's wrong?

308
00:31:00,797 --> 00:31:02,799
Se-ah, behind you.

309
00:31:05,468 --> 00:31:06,511
Is that…

310
00:31:07,428 --> 00:31:09,597
Is that what you guys have been seeing?

311
00:31:10,098 --> 00:31:11,349
But how can you

312
00:31:12,850 --> 00:31:14,310
also see that thing?

313
00:31:14,811 --> 00:31:15,645
Se-ah.

314
00:31:16,562 --> 00:31:17,981
I was afraid you might die,

315
00:31:19,315 --> 00:31:20,692
so I made a wish too.

316
00:31:27,240 --> 00:31:28,866
Don't come near me!

317
00:31:29,367 --> 00:31:30,785
-Turn around, Se-ah.
-Stay away!

318
00:31:30,868 --> 00:31:33,246
That's the only way I can save him!
Turn around!

319
00:31:34,789 --> 00:31:35,623
Ha-joon!

320
00:31:41,796 --> 00:31:42,964
You have to look now!

321
00:31:43,047 --> 00:31:44,340
Oh God, help me!

322
00:31:45,466 --> 00:31:46,759
Come on, look!

323
00:31:46,843 --> 00:31:48,011
Se-ah, help me!

324
00:31:50,179 --> 00:31:51,014
I see you.

325
00:31:55,476 --> 00:31:56,602
Haetsal!

326
00:31:57,478 --> 00:31:58,896
What's wrong? What?

327
00:31:59,397 --> 00:32:01,816
It found me. I have to fight my way out.

328
00:32:02,316 --> 00:32:03,276
Open the door again.

329
00:32:03,359 --> 00:32:05,653
Then you need to get out in three minutes!

330
00:32:05,737 --> 00:32:06,821
You know that, right?

331
00:34:09,902 --> 00:34:11,112
Se-ah!

332
00:34:14,365 --> 00:34:15,658
Se-ah, are you okay?

333
00:34:20,705 --> 00:34:23,332
We must go out that door. Run!

334
00:34:50,610 --> 00:34:51,777
Ha-young.

335
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,156
It's over now.

336
00:34:55,656 --> 00:34:56,866
We're alive.

337
00:35:14,884 --> 00:35:15,968
Brother-in-law.

338
00:35:22,475 --> 00:35:23,434
Se-ah, are you okay?

339
00:35:23,517 --> 00:35:27,021
I'm totally fine, so don't worry about me.

340
00:35:27,104 --> 00:35:28,981
Se-ah is okay now, right?

341
00:35:30,566 --> 00:35:31,901
Ha-young, that blood…

342
00:35:31,984 --> 00:35:33,527
So you do see it.

343
00:35:34,612 --> 00:35:35,863
She'll be okay for now,

344
00:35:35,947 --> 00:35:38,991
but I'm sorry to say
that it's not completely over yet.

345
00:35:39,992 --> 00:35:42,703
We only cut her thread to the other side
for a moment.

346
00:35:44,330 --> 00:35:46,082
To end this for good,

347
00:35:47,124 --> 00:35:49,126
we must find maehyung and get rid of it.

348
00:35:49,210 --> 00:35:50,336
What's with your arm?

349
00:35:50,419 --> 00:35:52,964
It's nothing. Don't fuss.
Let's deal with the kids first.

350
00:35:53,047 --> 00:35:55,466
Ha-joon, can you move Se-ah inside?

351
00:35:55,549 --> 00:35:56,384
Okay.

352
00:36:00,429 --> 00:36:01,555
Let me see your arm.

353
00:36:02,723 --> 00:36:04,308
See? I told you it's nothing.

354
00:36:06,102 --> 00:36:07,603
You call that nothing?

355
00:36:07,687 --> 00:36:10,523
Keep using that power,
and you'll never leave this house.

356
00:36:10,606 --> 00:36:12,275
You'll only make it harder.

357
00:36:12,775 --> 00:36:14,193
I know.

358
00:36:14,694 --> 00:36:17,613
I know, but can you watch the kids
while I treat my wounds?

359
00:36:21,867 --> 00:36:22,702
Okay?

360
00:37:01,741 --> 00:37:02,658
Na-ri!

361
00:37:03,576 --> 00:37:04,410
Na-ri!

362
00:37:06,495 --> 00:37:08,122
You still haven't gone home?

363
00:37:09,290 --> 00:37:10,124
No.

364
00:37:10,207 --> 00:37:12,168
You're here to see Geon-woo, aren't you?

365
00:37:12,251 --> 00:37:14,670
-Geon-woo's not in the ICU anymore.
-Sorry?

366
00:37:14,754 --> 00:37:17,506
He got better earlier,
so we moved him to a regular room.

367
00:37:18,466 --> 00:37:21,427
Oh my God, I'm so glad to hear that.

368
00:37:22,261 --> 00:37:23,429
When was this?

369
00:37:24,138 --> 00:37:26,640
It's been about an hour since he woke up.

370
00:37:27,141 --> 00:37:28,434
You can go visit him.

371
00:37:29,352 --> 00:37:30,895
Okay, I'll do that.

372
00:37:40,863 --> 00:37:42,073
This is me?

373
00:37:45,701 --> 00:37:47,536
I hate to say this,

374
00:37:47,620 --> 00:37:50,790
but Se-ah said
she couldn't bear to see you since then,

375
00:37:51,415 --> 00:37:52,583
so I came alone.

376
00:38:01,759 --> 00:38:03,761
Get to the point. Why did you call me?

377
00:38:07,264 --> 00:38:08,099
Scoot over.

378
00:38:19,693 --> 00:38:21,404
Were you going to make a wish?

379
00:38:24,865 --> 00:38:26,492
You didn't have to hit me!

380
00:38:27,284 --> 00:38:28,744
Don't ever do this again.

381
00:38:28,828 --> 00:38:30,996
You'll only make things harder
for your sister.

382
00:38:32,623 --> 00:38:36,127
Don't end up as another guest
and hurt Haetsal even more.

383
00:38:40,047 --> 00:38:42,216
Didn't you come
because you trust your sister?

384
00:38:42,299 --> 00:38:43,259
Am I wrong?

385
00:38:43,342 --> 00:38:45,302
Then trust her a little more.

386
00:38:47,096 --> 00:38:49,098
Man, I'm seriously begging you.

387
00:38:52,017 --> 00:38:52,935
Brother-in-law.

388
00:39:04,029 --> 00:39:05,865
Seriously, stop calling me that.

389
00:39:10,327 --> 00:39:11,495
A change of clothes.

390
00:39:11,579 --> 00:39:13,789
We need to burn yours,
so put them in there.

391
00:39:16,083 --> 00:39:16,917
I heard

392
00:39:17,418 --> 00:39:18,961
you injured your arm.

393
00:39:20,588 --> 00:39:21,714
I'm sorry.

394
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:25,217
It's because I didn't trust you
and looked back.

395
00:39:25,801 --> 00:39:29,180
I should be apologizing.
You came here, but I couldn't finish it.

396
00:39:29,263 --> 00:39:31,599
I had no idea what you'd been through,

397
00:39:31,682 --> 00:39:33,601
and I made it sound like it was easy.

398
00:39:33,684 --> 00:39:36,395
I shouldn't have let you see
something so horrible.

399
00:39:38,772 --> 00:39:41,025
It wasn't all horrible.

400
00:39:42,943 --> 00:39:45,362
I know this might sound silly,

401
00:39:47,114 --> 00:39:48,407
but it was

402
00:39:49,575 --> 00:39:52,578
nice to see my mom and dad again,
even if it was like that.

403
00:39:53,829 --> 00:39:55,498
-Se-ah.
-I know.

404
00:39:55,581 --> 00:39:57,124
I know it was all fake.

405
00:39:59,919 --> 00:40:01,754
-But still--
-It wasn't all fake.

406
00:40:02,505 --> 00:40:03,923
Your memories are there too.

407
00:40:04,423 --> 00:40:07,801
Memories so painful that you buried them
deep in your subconscious.

408
00:40:07,885 --> 00:40:11,430
I'm sure your mom,
who tried so hard to save you, was real.

409
00:40:11,514 --> 00:40:14,642
What kind of vile thing would use
even those memories against you?

410
00:40:14,725 --> 00:40:16,185
It's so annoying.

411
00:40:19,188 --> 00:40:20,147
Ha-young.

412
00:40:21,482 --> 00:40:24,151
Help me put an end to this
without any loose ends…

413
00:40:26,153 --> 00:40:30,032
and stop that girl
who was on the other side.

414
00:40:30,950 --> 00:40:32,535
Please.

415
00:40:35,371 --> 00:40:37,456
This app that you guys call Girigo is…

416
00:40:37,540 --> 00:40:38,415
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

417
00:40:39,959 --> 00:40:43,128
…in our terms,
a curse born from a vengeful spirit.

418
00:40:43,212 --> 00:40:44,755
To deal with it,

419
00:40:44,838 --> 00:40:47,216
we need to find and destroy the maehyung

420
00:40:47,299 --> 00:40:49,468
that connects our side
to the spirit's side.

421
00:40:49,552 --> 00:40:50,553
Maehyung?

422
00:40:50,636 --> 00:40:52,346
Yeah. Maehyung.

423
00:40:52,972 --> 00:40:56,433
"Mae" means "to bury,"
and "hyung" means "wicked."

424
00:40:56,517 --> 00:40:59,812
Objects that contain the power of a curse
are called maehyung.

425
00:41:01,730 --> 00:41:04,525
Remember the red phone
that was attached to your wrist?

426
00:41:04,608 --> 00:41:05,609
The one you saw there.

427
00:41:14,618 --> 00:41:15,452
Yes.

428
00:41:15,536 --> 00:41:17,913
You need to bring that
to this house, Se-ah.

429
00:41:17,997 --> 00:41:19,123
Must it be Se-ah?

430
00:41:21,208 --> 00:41:24,253
We have no choice.
She's the only one who can hold the phone.

431
00:41:24,837 --> 00:41:29,008
Se-ah's the only one connected to me,
the vengeful spirit, and both realms.

432
00:41:48,611 --> 00:41:49,987
Brother-in-law.

433
00:46:19,882 --> 00:46:22,551
Subtitle translation by: Sung In Jang
